{
  "stem": "9489.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and he says, he wasn't made by Jew and then when he grow up in this area, he want to go with Jewish girls.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They told him [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You understand?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was not-- not here, not there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he denied the father, you understand?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And according Jewish law, if the mother's not Jewish, he's not a Jew.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he was [INAUDIBLE], so he took revenge.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyways, that's what he told me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You believe it?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Not, yes, not.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But that's the way the old German guy-- and he took me to his country house.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He showed me the [INAUDIBLE] there, and he kept me for three days like a king.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I even got drunk with-- they got apple cider.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's so strong, he light it up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "A match, it burns.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And, you know, that's the way he told me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "In [INAUDIBLE], they took me through the Alps to Milan.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And in Milan, they took me into the partisans work for the-- for the Haganah.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "From the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Who knows?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Was all different parties.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But everybody got a different job, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then they got me in the papers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I got black and white to prove.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You saw it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, I mean, I got the papers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "For this [INAUDIBLE] Street and [INAUDIBLE] Street, I got the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "For Israel, they couldn't get.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And to the [INAUDIBLE] from Rome-- from Milan.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And even after surgery, when I got-- the surgery was done to me, Professor Mazzero.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He was one from the highest fascist professor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was a private clinic.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they brought him from Israel, Haganah, to be with the surgery.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "A Jewish woman doctor from Milan in [INAUDIBLE] was mine surgery.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What from the poison, what was it.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
